      <scopecontent id="ref4">
         <head>Description of the Material</head>
         <p>USGS 7.5" topographic quadrangle maps of New York related to his Yale dissertation, "Marine paleoecology of the Upper Devonian Genesee Group of New York." Also, 2 field notebooks and the locality register from his dissertation.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
